column2: Activate this tactic to temporarily summon chill inducers that will chill invaders at the objective.
Veteran Gloss the Gold Phoenix Loot Box[pl:Boxes"]"
Burn tendrils and avoid unexploded shot before time runs out!
Champion Ark the White Tiger Loot Box[pl:Boxes"]"
Shoot as many target dummies as you can before time runs out!
Gaining stealth blinds nearby foes. Blinding a foe siphons health from them.
Traits are now unlocked. Spending hero points in specializations earns you traits. Once unlocked, you can select them in the build tab for your specialization.
<c=@flavor>Crafted in the style of the Teku Nuhoch Kaana, Pahua.</c>

Drop a smoke bomb when you are disabled.
Disables include stun, daze, knockback, pull, knockdown, sink, float, launch, taunt, and fear.
Gain access to a network of regional merchants across Tyria with a limited supply of rare goods for trade, and increase your party's swiftness bonus in cities to 15%%.
<c=@abilitytype>Physical.</c> Take the form of a massive juggernaut, reducing the damage you take and the duration of incoming movement-impeding conditions.
Veteran Narf the Gold Wolf Loot Box[pl:Boxes"]"
The water spirit teleports to your location and then heals you and nearby allies.
Not yet trained. Click to view in the training panel.
<c=@abilitytype>Shout.</c> Heal yourself and allies in a cone in front of you.
This jungle dolyak finisher box contains the jungle dolyak finisher, dragonite ore, empyreal fragments, obsidian shards, and mystic clovers.

Inner Harbor:
Find a shelf below the garden island.

Commodore's Quarters:
Head up the ramp between crate and barrel.
Increase chance to find rare materials from mining, logging, and harvesting by 16%%.
Increase chance to find rare materials from mining, logging, and harvesting by 12%%.

Gain 120 Condition Damage When Health above 90%%
+10%% Experience from Kills

Eastern Ward:
There's no location too secure for a karka.
Your conditions last longer, and your damage is increased.

Gain 60 Precision When Health above 90%%
+10%% Experience from Kills
You've unlocked your profession skill. Press F1 to appear near an enemy and steal from it. The stolen-item skill slot (F2) then changes depending on the creature you stole from.
Champion Blade the White Shark Loot Box[pl:Boxes"]"
Increase chance to find rare materials from mining, logging, and harvesting by 20%%.
Used in the manufacturing of fancy furniture.
You cannot join this game mode because you or someone in your party has too low of a PvP rank.
Healing Increase to Others per Attribute
Champion Sleepy the Black Bear Loot Box[pl:Boxes"]"
Healing to other allies is increased by 10%%.
Grants a small amount of experience. Trade 20 writs to Miyani in Lion's Arch for a tome of knowledge.

Sharkmaw Cavern:
Someone swore they saw a karka walk through a wall.
